OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News London Annette
OL,7,FDore said: "I don't think I'll ever,
OL,8,Fever get over it because I sat through
OL,9,Fthose treatments and held her hand and
OL,10,Fshe screamed - she screamed.
OL,12,F"Those treatments were harrowing to
OL,13,Fput a needle through somebody into
OL,14,Ftheir lungs, to draw fluid off almost
OL,15,Fevery day.
OL,17,F"And she'd squeeze my hands and she'd
OL,18,Fscream."
