OL,6,FThe 2,527-page report documents a
OL,7,F"catalogue of failures" which had
OL,8,F"catastrophic" consequences, not only
OL,9,Famong people infected with
OL,10,Fcontaminated blood and blood products,
OL,11,Fbut also their loved ones.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak is expected
OL,14,Fto make an apology in the House of
OL,15,FCommons later on Monday.
OL,17,FAnnette, who lives in Borehamwood,
OL,18,Fsaid an apology wouldn't bring her
OL,19,Fmother back, adding: "They always
OL,20,Fapologize, that's the problem. It
OL,21,Fdoesn't feel real.
