OL,6,F"I'm not the only person. There are
OL,7,Fpeople that have lost their lives with
OL,8,Fchildren - children now without either
OL,9,Fparent.
OL,11,F"The trickle affect it has and the
OL,12,Fimpact it has on families - for
OL,13,Fexample my father died (from an
OL,14,Funrelated condition) a year after my
OL,15,Fmum in the same month, and both of
OL,16,Fthem were only 54 years of age."
