OL,6,FMore than 30,000 people were infected
OL,7,Fwith deadly viruses while they were
OL,8,Freceiving NHS care between the 1970s
OL,9,Fand 1990s, in a disaster described by
OL,10,Finquiry chairman Sir Brian Langstaff
OL,11,Fas a "calamity".
OL,13,FSir Brian said "the scale of what
OL,14,Fhappened is horrifying", with more
OL,15,Fthan 3,000 people dead as a result and
OL,16,Fsurvivors battling for decades to
OL,17,Funcover the truth.
