OL,6,FSpeaking about her mother's rapid
OL,7,Fdecline in health Annette Dore said:
OL,8,F"We watched her decline. After the
OL,9,Ffirst year she was getting
OL,10,Fincreasingly tired.
OL,12,F"I just remember the day that she was
OL,13,Fleaving the house because I got home
OL,14,Ffrom work, and I went into her room,
OL,15,Fand she was just breathing, really
OL,16,Fheavy.
OL,18,F"And her whole chest, it was like it
OL,19,Fwas rattling."
