OL,6,FMuch of the responsibility for
OL,7,Ffailures identified in the report lie
OL,8,Fwith successive governments, which
OL,9,Ffailed to act in order to save face
OL,10,Fand expense, the inquiry said, with
OL,11,Fthe current Government criticised for
OL,12,Ffailing to act immediately on
OL,13,Frecommendations around compensation
OL,14,Fwhich were made last year.
OL,16,FMinisters have earmarked around #10
OL,17,Fbillion for a compensation package for
OL,18,Fthose affected, which is expected to
OL,19,Fbe announced on Tuesday or Wednesday.
